  "3165460": {
    "name": "Isles & Tiles",
    "steam_appid": 3165460,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从大海中抬升出岛屿并建设你的领地！《板块群岛》是一款回合制资源管理游戏，你需要在平衡岛屿扩张、领地发展和资源采集的同时，应对居民需求和卡牌抽取带来的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从基础的核心卡组出发，通过探索赢得游戏的不同路径来解锁新卡牌、事件、成就和游戏模式！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165460/extras/805b03233c7901167b5bacf1d068eb85.webp?t=1762296851\" width=626 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165460/extras/5b179d25830a2c77ce6c99a753327ae4.poster.avif?t=1762296851\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165460/extras/5b179d25830a2c77ce6c99a753327ae4.webm?t=1762296851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165460/extras/5b179d25830a2c77ce6c99a753327ae4.mp4?t=1762296851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >塑造一座岛屿 —— 使用你抽取到的卡牌勾勒海岸线并建设你的领地。每座岛屿都独一无二，你可以随时调整地形以适应需求。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理你的资源 —— 从少量基础资源开始，逐步建造你所需的设施。需要更多木材？培育一片森林并建造伐木场，或是从板块中抬升出山脉来开采石料。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >平衡你的需求 —— 领地的初期建设很简单，但随着时间的推移你必须权衡居民的需求和愿望。你将会如何抉择？</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165460/extras/1405ac75a5de3339de312d1255a613bd.webp?t=1762296851\" width=626 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165460/extras/863b27cd63fcc72510905e12db197a2c.poster.avif?t=1762296851\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165460/extras/863b27cd63fcc72510905e12db197a2c.webm?t=1762296851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165460/extras/863b27cd63fcc72510905e12db197a2c.mp4?t=1762296851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁传奇卡牌 —— 从基础的核心卡组开始，你可以逐步解锁百余张全新卡牌。收集胜利点数来取得新的卡牌，或是将你最爱的卡牌升级为传奇闪卡！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种策略与目标 —— 每一局游戏都独一无二！通过发现新卡牌来改变你的游戏策略，解锁新机制、新资源甚至新的获胜途径。专注于发展人口，或是抛开领地的殖民需求专心打造你的理想岛屿——你说了算！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165460/extras/a4dd0ed076a2580e975b35ca9b5383b0.webp?t=1762296851\" width=626 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165460/extras/129da668c8811bea20e6d7c410318f68.poster.avif?t=1762296851\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165460/extras/129da668c8811bea20e6d7c410318f68.webm?t=1762296851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165460/extras/129da668c8811bea20e6d7c410318f68.mp4?t=1762296851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获取强大的遗物 —— 随着游戏的进行，你将会发现能够改变游戏规则的强大遗物，开启全新策略或选择。不会有两次完全相同的游戏体验！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作出关键抉择 —— 你的岛民们会时不时请你作出重要决策，这些决策将会影响游戏进程。是私藏魔法遗物还是用其造福众生？由你定夺。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《板块群岛》的灵感来自《筑梦颂》、《卡卡颂》、《卡坦岛》等经典版图搭建游戏。在原声布塔尼亚民谣音乐的陪伴下，建设你的完美领地、解锁新卡牌、调整你的卡组并作出关键决策！</p>",
